## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all industry practices or recent developments in corporate finance. The data primarily reflects U.S. firms and may not be fully applicable to firms in different regulatory or economic environments. Additionally, the analysis does not account for firm-specific factors that might influence cash holding strategies.

